@jiangsshijie Her face is stiff, full of worry and rage waiting to be unleashed. She quickly cools down: she doesn't mean to bring any negative vibes to Jiang Yanli... She should talk of something happy instead, something that'd make her smile! Why can't she be smarter when it comes to people?
